ivardefs.name: code
ivardefs.desc: An error code, from a specified code system, which details why the claim could not be adjudicated.

ivardefs.name: detailSequence
ivardefs.desc: The sequence number of the detail within the line item submitted which contains the error. This value is omitted when the error occurs outside of the item structure.

ivardefs.name: itemSequence
ivardefs.desc: The sequence number of the line item submitted which contains the error. This value is omitted when the error occurs outside of the item structure.

ivardefs.name: subDetailSequence
ivardefs.desc: The sequence number of the sub-detail within the detail within the line item submitted which contains the error. This value is omitted when the error occurs outside of the item structure.

properties.desc: Errors encountered during the processing of the adjudication.
